## What is Serverless?
In your current MERN stack, your Node.js server is "always on," waiting for a request. In Serverless:

- API Gateway acts as the "Front Door" (replaces Nginx).
- AWS Lambda acts as the "Function" (replaces your Node.js backend).
- DynamoDB acts as the "Database" (replaces MongoDB).

-------------------------
